data.description: This one level home features a split bedroom plan and offers an oversized kitchen. The bedroom sizes and closets are generous. The kitchen features lots of counter space for cooking and open for entertaining. The backyard is fenced with a pond and home also features a carport. The crawl space is encapsulated and the energy bills are low. Check this out today!
